as
I
am
in
my
father's."
"But
then,
to
be
an
old
maid
at
last,
like
Miss
Bates!"
"That
is
as
formidable
an
image
as
you
could
present,
Harriet;
and
if
I
thought
I
should
ever
be
like
Miss
Bates!
so
