and
too
silly
to
suit
me;
but,
in
general,
she
is
very
much
to
the
taste
of
every
body,
though
single
and
though
poor.
Poverty
certainly
has
not
contracted
her
mind:
I
really
believe,
if
she
had
only
a
shilling
in
the
world,
she
would
be
very
likely
to
give
away
sixpence
of
it;
and
nobody
is
afraid
of
her:
that
